{
  "stem": "10859.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, we starved a little.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But-- but we didn't die from [INAUDIBLE]-- from hunger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, we couldn't die, because we still had potatoes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, and if you have potatoes, and you have beans, and you have carrots, and you have all the other vegetables from the ground, you can survive.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After-- now also, at the same time, when we were living there quietly in that village, and also the other-- the next-- Trochenbrod, the next little town-- at the same time, they killed already tens of thousands of people in the big cities.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we didn't know about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody know what goes on in 10 mile-- kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First of all, we were not allowed to walk nowhere or to drive anywhere, because we didn't have no transportation anyway.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had to wear either a Magen David or either a yellow sign, like a piece of rag, you know, pinned in to the front and to the back.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For the purpose, if you walk around somewhere, and a German or a Ukrainian will see you, he can kill you.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he'll know that you are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Otherwise, how would he know you were Jewish?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The whole idea was just to make sure that easy to kill 'em.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's all the combinations what they did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and one day, suddenly came in-- I don't remember if it was one or two Germans-- that's all-- to our place, to our village.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was about-- about 20 or maybe 30 Ukrainian with the rifles-- everyone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These went to each house and said, there is a order from the German government to leave your place and go to the next place.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Take whatever you can with you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We don't care.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
